fnlColorVariantData.catDescription:
Nike is a leading global brand founded in the U.S., known for its footwear, apparel, and accessories. Initially focused on athletic shoes, it offers products across running, basketball, training, and lifestyle categories. Nike, driven by its “Just Do It” mentality, focuses on innovation and high-quality materials, continually evolving to meet the needs of athletes and active individuals. AJIO’s range of Nike products features apparel and accessories crafted with precision. Whether you’re searching for men’s Nike shoes or other essentials, AJIO has everything to fulfil your needs.

Let’s explore the standout pieces from Nike's exclusive collection at the Nike store on AJIO.

Unleash Comfort with Stylish Nike Sneakers

Nike sneakers are made for those who cherish quality and durability. Whether running errands or on the go, these sneakers will provide the perfect fit while still allowing you to be comfortable for long periods. Shop on AJIO for a range of Nike sneakers that seamlessly combine comfort with sleek designs.

The Ultimate Nike Sweatshirt for Cosy Days

Stay warm and stylish with the perfect Nike sweater. Made for comfort and designed for those chilly days, this classic can be paired with jeans or sweatpants. Check out their new styles and all the colours and sizes available online at AJIO.

Layer Up with a Versatile Nike Hoodie

Prepare for the season with AJIO's Nike hoodie. This hoodie is an essential for all wardrobes and uniquely combines comfort, style, and warmth. With an extensive range of designs and materials, it represents a great way to complete a casual look.

Perfect Pairing: Nike Shorts for Ultimate Comfort

For a relaxed yet stylish look, opt for Nike shorts. Made to provide flexibility and breathability, Nike shorts are perfect for both workouts and casual wear. Stay cool and comfortable no matter where your day takes you, with the unmatched quality of Nike shorts.

Step into Style with Premium Nike Shoes

Nike shoes are built to deliver top-tier performance, long-lasting durability, and comfort for every step you take. Whether you’re running, walking, or just hanging out, Nike shoes are built to last. Browse through various styles and find your ideal fit, including Nike women's shoes at AJIO, which offer function and flair.

Sporty and Trendy: Nike T-Shirts for Every Occasion

Upgrade your casual wardrobe with a trendy Nike t-shirt. Featuring breathable materials and stylish designs, Nike t-shirts are perfect for any occasion, whether you're working out or heading out for a casual day. Choose your favourite style and enjoy a comfortable, athletic fit built to last.

Complete Your Look with Nike at AJIO

Nike is renowned for its high-quality, reliable products and innovative designs. At AJIO, you will find a wide range of Nike products to fill your needs. From versatile apparel to premium footwear, Nike’s collection on AJIO has everything you need to elevate your everyday look.

tncListData: Top Shopper contest will be live during the duration of AJIO All Stars Sale or AASS
The contest is only open to users who have successfully placed an order on AJIO - either through prepaid (or) through cash on delivery (COD) mode
AJIO shall not charge any amount from any user for taking part in this contest
The rewards mentioned as the prize for each slot can change based on any external factors out of AJIO's control
If user places multiple orders during same slot, those order values will be added & total order value is considered
If two users placed order for same amount, the user who placed order earlier will be considered as the winner
Please note that the net order value will be considered for each user after reducing the amount for any cancellations/returns
A user whose name appears on top of leaderboard does not guarantee reward. The final winners will be chosen by AJIO after considering cancellations & returns
eventHowToParticipateContentList: Top Shopper contest is live for users during the AJIO Big Bold Sale or BBS
Each day is divided into 24 slots of 4 hours each & for each slot, the top shopper(based on net order value) will be considered as the winner
All users placing orders during the contest duration will be considered for the participation
If user places multiple orders during same slot, those order values will be added & total order value        is considered
If two users placed order for same amount, the user who placed order earlier will be considered as          the winner
Please note that the net order value will be considered for each user after reducing the amount for          any cancellations/returns
Refer to the complete terms & conditions list for this contest using the link given below
topShopperHowToWinList: Winners from daily sale events are eligible to the lucky draw for grand prize.
Lucky draw list will be automatically updated as soon as a sale event is over.
At the end of the Big Bold Sale the draw will happen.
The winners will be contacted by our executives for further procedures & reward distribution.

reasonScreenConfig.heading: Please read carefully before proceeding
reasonScreenConfig.readPolicy:
Your account will be deleted in 30 days and you will lose access to all your data and order history. You will not be able to recover your account in future and will be logged out after your confirmation. You won’t be able to use your Email and Phone Number linked with this account to login or create new account for those 30 days.

If you decide later that you want to start ordering from us again, or if you would like to use websites features that require an account, you’ll need to create a new account. .

Ajio will retain your transaction history.
